 exit
 
 frame .front6 foldup |COLOUR| at xmin.front5 ymax width 20 height 5
 
 button .red'RED' Tooltip 'ce element red colour' call |Enhance ce colour red|
 button .Brown'BROWN' Tooltip 'ce element Brown colour' call |Enhance ce colour Brown|
 button .white'WHITE' Tooltip 'ce element white colour' call |Enhance ce colour white|
